replyContent: Hi happy that you are enjoying the app.I just did a quick calculation. From chapter 9 tables 5 12 THHN, area = 0.0133 From chapter 9 tables note 4 raceway 24 in. or less fill is 60% From chapter 9 tables 4 For 1 in PVC - 40. at 60% fill, area = 0.499 Minimum number of 12 THHN in a 1 in. PVC Schedule 40 (0.499 / 0.0133 = 37.51) same as app
